data.description:
Must show this inviting 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home. This beautiful layout gives a sense of warmth and comfort, with a thoughtfully designed layout that maximizes both functionality and aesthetic appeal. The bedrooms, each offering a cozy retreat, provide ample space for relaxation and personalization. The heart of the home is the well-equipped kitchen, featuring a convenient breakfast bar. Nice size master bedroom with en-suite bathroom with a large walking closet. House is located just 9 mins away from Joe Pool Lake and major highways. Pictures were enhanced to make the grass appear greener.
Seller will not make repairs.
